# Placeholder so the directory exists in fresh checkouts.
#
# A user-global Claude Code SessionStart hook redirects errors into
# `.remember/logs/hook-errors.log` under the project root. The redirect
# fails noisily (`/bin/sh: ...: No such file or directory`) when the
# parent directory is absent on a fresh clone. Tracking the directory
# via this `.gitkeep` is the smallest fix that makes the redirect
# succeed without committing any actual log content.
#
# `.remember/logs/*` is git-ignored except for this file (see the
# repo-root `.gitignore`), so logs stay local-only.
